    <name>Danceinterpreter</name>
    <summary>Utility for displaying song infos</summary>

    <description>
        <p>The Danceinterpreter is a utility to display songs and their according dances at ballroom dance events</p>
        <p>It currently contains three source modes</p>
        <ol>
            <li>M3U / M3U8 files with references to local mp3 files</li>
            <li>A connection to a running Traktor Pro instance</li>
            <li>Manually added songs and static dance labels</li>
        </ol>
    </description>

